---
layout: base.njk
title: Split Rim Offset Calculator
navActive: offset
---
<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6">
<div class="lg:flex-shrink-0">
<div id="offset-calculator" class="bg-[--color-calc-bg] border-2 border-[--color-calc-border] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-6 w-full max-w-[620px]">
<h3 class="text-base font-bold bg-[--color-calc-heading] text-[--color-text-dark] px-2 py-1 -mx-4 -mt-4 mb-4 rounded-t-md">Wheel Details (3-piece wheel / split rim)</h3>
<form onsubmit="calculator.calculate(this); return false;" onreset="calculator.clearall();">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="oldOuter" class="font-bold text-[#C00] whitespace-nowrap">Original <em class="uppercase not-italic">outer</em> lip width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="oldOuter" name="oldOuter" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FCD116] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="newOuter" class="font-bold text-[#060] whitespace-nowrap">New <em class="uppercase not-italic">outer</em> lip width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="newOuter" name="newOuter" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FCD116] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="oldInner" class="font-bold text-[#C00] whitespace-nowrap">Original <em class="uppercase not-italic">inner</em> barrel width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="oldInner" name="oldInner" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FF8C00] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="newInner" class="font-bold text-[#060] whitespace-nowrap">New <em class="uppercase not-italic">inner</em> barrel width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="newInner" name="newInner" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FF8C00] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="wheelWidth" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Original wheel width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="wheelWidth" name="wheelWidth" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FFE4B5] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="offset" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Original wheel offset</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="offset" name="offset" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FFE4B5] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="spacers" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Spacers</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="spacers" name="spacers" size="4" value="0" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FFE4B5] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center py-4">
  <input type="submit" class="button" value="Calculate" />&nbsp;
  <input type="reset" class="button" value="Reset" />
</div>
</form>

<table id="offset-calculator-result" class="results w-full text-sm border border-[--color-table-border]">
<tr><th></th><th>Original</th><th>New</th></tr>
<tr><th>Wheel Width <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span></th>
<td id="old-width">-</td><td id="new-width">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Wheel Offset <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td id="old-offset">-</td><td id="new-offset">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Overall Offset <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="overall-offset">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Arch clearance <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="arch-diff">-</td></tr>
<tr><th>Strut clearance <span class="text-xs font-normal">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span></th>
<td>-</td><td id="strut-diff">-</td></tr>
</table>

<div id="comparison" class="results"></div>
<div id="resource-links" class="results text-right text-xs"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="description" class="lg:flex-1 min-w-0 text-[--color-text-dark] text-base leading-relaxed">
<h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">About the Split Rim Offset Calculator</h2>
<p><img src="/images/split-rim.jpg" width="300" alt="Split Rim (3-piece wheel)" class="rounded shadow-md mb-4" /></p>
<p class="mb-4">
  The split rim offset calculator allows you to calculate the new width and offset of your 3-piece (split rim)
  wheels when you change the inner barrel and/or outer lip.</p>
<p class="mb-4">Here are some examples that will automatically complete the calculator form to help you get started:</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-4">
  <li><a href="javascript:calculator.demo('split-rim', 1);" class="text-[--color-link] hover:text-[--color-link-hover] underline">Adding a larger outer lip to an 8J et32 wheel.</a></li>
  <li><a href="javascript:calculator.demo('split-rim', 2);" class="text-[--color-link] hover:text-[--color-link-hover] underline">Changing both inner and outer sections of a 10J et45 wheel.</a></li>
</ul>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">* Note that you do not have to fill in all the fields for the calculator to give you a result.</p>
</div>
</div>
